data.title: Justin and Hailey Bieber's love story began at a fan event in 2009, where 12-year-old Hailey, accompanied by her father Stephen Baldwin,...
data.meta_description:
1,173 likes, 12 comments - meawwofficial on May 10, 2024: "Justin and Hailey Bieber's love story began at a fan event in 2009, where 12-year-old Hailey, accompanied by her father Stephen Baldwin, crossed paths with Justin Bieber. Hailey later shared in an interview with Vogue that while she wasn't a superfan, she found Justin cute like many others. However, due to their age difference, she didn't think much about it initially. Their paths crossed again in 2011 at the New York City premiere of "Never Say Never," where Stephen Baldwin brought Hailey along. Despite their initial encounter, Hailey and Justin's relationship evolved over the years. By 2018, after a whirlwind romance, Justin proposed to Hailey during a vacation in the Bahamas. Fast forward to May 2024, the couple shared exciting news on Instagram, revealing that Hailey was pregnant with their first child. Both Justin and Hailey posted touching photos and videos capturing the special moment. Hailey was adorned in a beautiful white dress and veil, proudly displaying her baby bump while embraced by Justin, showcasing their joy and anticipation for the arrival of their baby.
